title: D'Arcy Carden | The FBI Investigated Whether Trump Worked for Russia: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at accusations that Trump worked for a foreign government and the federal government’s ongoing shutdown.

Then, Seth talks to The Good Place's D'Arcy Carden, who also takes a few more questions backstage just for the podcast.
